    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Sorry, didn't notice the replies. The configure widget has no props on a page reload, the data is just in the search state in the url. Shouldn't it still be added to the search state even though configure is empty on a page load?\r\n\r\nI can try to make an example monday if that doesn't help.",
