    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We made the Configure widget so that there's only one way to have parameters applied: you have to set props on it.\r\n\r\nSo the best option is to read them from the state then forward them to the Configure widget. I understand this is then not consistent with other widgets like Menu which will take the refined value into account.\r\n\r\nWe will have to revisit this later on then.",
